column2: SELECT   ra_BCG, dec_BCG FROM MyDB.BCG_SF_IN  OPEN my_cursor  WHILE(#=#) BEGIN   FETCH NEXT from my_cursor into    @ra_BCG, @dec_BCG     IF (@@fetch_status < #) break      INSERT MYDB.BCG_SF_OUT      SELECT   @ra_BCG, @dec_BCG,               p.objID, p.ra, p.dec                gz.spiral, gz.elliptical, gz.uncertain,                p.bpt               FROM   dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(@ra_BCG,@dec_BCG,#/#) n, Galaxy p     JOIN Photoz  As z ON z.objid = p.objid   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid   JOIN zooSpec AS gz ON gz.objid = p.objid   JOIN emissionLinesPort  As z ON z.objid = p.objid    WHERE n.objid=p.objid         END  CLOSE my_cursor DEALLOCATE my_cursor
